<h3>Required Technology</h3>

<ul>
    <li>PDF scanner app for your phone (or other device) for submitting
      homework. Scan-to-pdf capability is a built-in feature of Android and
      Apple phones; there are also many free apps
    <li>Any device with a webcam and microphone and running Zoom for
    online class attendance and office hours (if Zoom class meetings and
    office hours become necessary)
<!--<li>Respondus Lockdown Browser running on a Windows or MacOS machine
  with webcam and microphone for exams (if remote exams become
  necessary)-->
</ul>
